<plot>St. Louis, Missouri has ranked number 1 or 2 in the country as the most dangerous city in the United States. 'Where do we go from here?' That is the question this documentary tries to examine. Off The Record is about life on the streets of St. Louis's roughest neighborhoods. It takes a look at the problems of violence, sex, and gang life in St. Louis. Through the eyes of the people who live there.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?407715</url></doc>
